Indie Rock Night at Whelan's

Don't miss this exciting showcase of local indie talent featuring up-and-coming Dublin bands The Northside Rebels and Electric Dawn.

Location: Whelan's, 25 Wexford St, Dublin 2

Date: March 25, 2024

Time: 19:30 - 23:00

Tickets: €15 advance / €18 door

Full bar service available
